”’Щ@8bc23f88a7f61bc64c8cada3c5adeb62fc2d1e099ee7c486bbf3557f87df162cЪyTitle: This week in Nushell #263
Path: Nushell
Content:
ayax79 implemented tons of Polars-related improvements (
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/13799] added expression support for 
``polars cumulative``
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/13798] reorganized Polars commands
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/13783] added expression support for 
``polars str-slice``
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/13782] added expression support for 
``polars str-lengths``
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/13781] renamed 
``polars concatenate``
 and added expression support
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/13769] added expression support for 
``polars contains``
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/13767] added expression support for 
``polars strftime``
) and a few HTTP improvements too (
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/13791] used String::contains instead of exact match for http request content types
 and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/13731] fixed string values passing their content-type correctly on http requests with a body
)
IanManske 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/13515] added an error on non-zero exit statuses
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/13751] used 
``IntoValue``
 in config code
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/13744] implemented 
``IntoValue``
 for more types
devyn 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/13745] removed bincode and used MessagePack instead for plugin custom values
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/13652] made 
``tee``
 work more nicely with non-collections
fdncred 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/13797] updated the latest reedline
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/13792] fixed an issue with find not working with symbols that should be escaped
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/13788] removed config use_grid_icons and moved it to a parameter of the grid command
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/13764] added version and path to plugin executable help
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/13737] fixed --ide-ast when there are errors
WindSoilder 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/13795] made a user-friendly message when 
``use_grid_icons``
 is used in config
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/13752] prevented panic on 
``detect columns``
 with 
``--guess``
 flag
sholderbach 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/13793] fixed 
``serde``
 feature selection in 
``nu-protocol``
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/13749] removed unneeded 
``serde``
 feature on 
``byte-unit``
 dep
hustcer 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/13775] added aarch64-unknown-linux-musl and armv7-unknown-linux-musleabihf release targets
cptpiepmatz 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/13761] added 
``#[nu_value(rename = "...")]``
 as helper attribute on members for derive macros
JTopanotti 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/13701] refactored send_request in client.rs
