[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell.github.io/pull/1543] added a blog announcement for Discord Showcase
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell.github.io/pull/1542] updated the Plugin Chapter
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell.github.io/pull/1508] added a dropdown for docs on the main page
lfrancke 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell.github.io/pull/1540] fixed broken links
